1.Mt s lnh vi linux (ubuntu) dnh cho ngi mi bt u, u tin bn bt
terminal ln:
- sudo (lnh chy vi quyn admin): vs sudo apt-get update ( cp nht)
- cd (change directory) : truy cp vo mt th mc vd : cd Pangolin
- mkdir : lnh to th mc vd: mkdir build
1.1: Cu hnh khuyn ngh : core i5 8G ram v ci phn vng ubuntu khong 300G
2.Ghi ch qu trnh chy DSO code
- b1: clone DSO v : https://github.com/JakobEngel/dso
sau lm theo hng dn, ci libopencv, ziplib.
- b2: clone pangolin : https://github.com/stevenlovegrove/Pangolin
- b3: ti ffmpeg-3.4.1, nu cha c yasm th ci yasm
- b4: gii nn ffmpeg-3.4.1.tar.bz2 (tar -xvjf xxx.tar.bz2), sau vo th mc
ffmpeg-3.4.1 (cd ffmpeg-3.4.1) g ./configure --enable-nonfree --enable-pic
--enable-shared
- b5: ci qtbase ( sudo apt install qtbase5-dev )
- b6: ci opencv 2.4.11 https://gist.github.com/dynamicguy/3d1fce8dae65e765f7c4
- b7: ci pangolin, trc , phi ci glew ( sudo apt-get install libglew-dev
) . ci pangolin, u tin, to th mc build cd Pangolin
mkdir build
sau truy cp vo th mc build v g cc lnh cmake sau
cd build
sudo cmake ..
sudo cmake --build .
cui cng, vn trong th mc build, g : sudo make install
- b8: build dso : to th mc build trong fild dso : cd dso mkdir build
truy cp vo th mc build: cd build dng lnh sudo chy cmake : sudo cmake ..
(du cch trc hai du chm l tht y) tip theo g: sudo make -j4 (4 l s
lung ca cpu) nu khng dng lnh sudo, s khng th build ra file bin c, nu
nh trong file build ca bn khng c file bin, th bn phi to li. Vo file build ri
g lnh : sudo rm CMakeCache.txt sau quay li sudo cmake ..
- b9: download th vin tp tin d liu test (cc bn xem ng link trong link git
ca dso, sau lm theo hng dn)
bin/dso_dataset \
files=XXXXX/sequence_XX/images.zip \
calib=XXXXX/sequence_XX/camera.txt \
gamma=XXXXX/sequence_XX/pcalib.txt \
vignette=XXXXX/sequence_XX/vignette.png \
preset=0 \
mode=0
XXXXX l ng dn n file d liu ti v, ch gii nn d liu ra.
Lu v cc li c th gp.

sudo apt-get install libqt5concurrent5
sudo apt-get install libqt5test5
sudo apt-get install libqt5core5a
sudo apt-get install libqt5opengl5
sudo apt-get install qtdeclarative5-dev

nhng dng ny vo phn # optional libraries
